     <div type="notice_to_the_reader">
   <p>Gentle Reader, where you see this title THE ARGVMENTS,
printed above almost of every page, there read, OF THE RE<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>VELATION.
And where you see, OF THE REVELATI<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ON,
there read, THE ARGVMENTS.</p>
   <p>Good Reader vnderstand, that this larger <hi>Scholion</hi> fol<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>lowing,
in order of time, was written afore these <hi>Argu<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ments:</hi>
as thou maist perceive in the reading.</p>
